com.taliter.fiscal.port.rxtx

Class RXTXFiscalPortSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.taliter.fiscal.port.rxtx.RXTXFiscalPortSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FiscalPortSource, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class RXTXFiscalPortSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements FiscalPortSource, java.lang.Cloneable
    An RXTXFiscalPort factory.

    Most of the parameters of this class are defined in the gnu.io package.

    Defaults:

    portName = null;
    appName = "RXTXFiscalPort";
    openTimeout = 2000; // In milliseconds.
    baudRate = 9600;
    dataBits = SerialPort.DATABITS_8;
    stopBits = SerialPort.STOPBITS_1;
    parity = SerialPort.PARITY_NONE;
    flowControl = SerialPort.FLOWCONTROL_NONE;

    The set of available serial port names can be obtained via RXTXFiscalPort.getPortNames().
